Our group member Liang Shi is is elected as the [Rising Star of Light (PhD track)](https://www.nature.com/documents/2022_Rising_Stars_of_Light_Winners.pdf) by [Nature Light Science & Applications](https://www.nature.com/lsa). Congratulations!